reviews.title: Good but...
reviews.comment: If I go deep within the previews without buying a pack the app crashes and blackens my wallpaper. Pls fix other wise the apps nice. Since I don\'t know all the packs I suggest you add the Mauser C96 and a ballistic knife correct me if it\'s in a pack. My phone is an Alcatel Glory 2 on Android jellybean.
reviews.author: Nuki Atienza

reviews.title: Great game
reviews.comment: I love this game. I just think abit more guns should be free. Also i reckon that we should have like laser guns or something. But yeah. Great game 5 stars.
reviews.author: Nicholas Van Den Berg

reviews.title: Good
reviews.comment: I would really like to see the basic guns (free guns) re done cuz there is a noticeable difference in graphics between the expansions and the free stuff. Please look into this.
reviews.author: Chris Moore

reviews.title: Very fun but updates are rare
reviews.comment: Very cool gun simulator and lots of different guns but there are graphical errors but most minor, the biggest problem is how it is rarely ever updated while on IOS they\'re multiple gun packs ahead
reviews.author: david rhue

reviews.title: Has some issues
reviews.comment: On some weapons there is an issue where the flashlight\'s light makes part of the barrel dissapear. Also the ios version is miles more updated. I would like to see more android updates
reviews.author: Jake Lauer

reviews.title: Needs coin earning
reviews.comment: Everytime I use a gun and do some cool tricks but when I exit the gun I still don\'t have any coins. Pls fix!
reviews.author: Austin Alotta

reviews.title: Innacurate
reviews.comment: The 1911 doesn\'t have a slide release,  the mac 10 doesn\'t have a semi/auto switch. The m4 and glock 18 don\'t chamber after hitting the slide release after inserting a new mag. This is just what I saw on the few I tried.
reviews.author: Grant Golden

reviews.title: Great app
reviews.comment: I love this game with the expansion packs it relay makes it bettered than all the other gun Sims and it works on Samsung galaxy tab 2 so I\'m good with it can\'t wait for urban warfare
reviews.author: Alex Larkin

reviews.title: Needs an update
reviews.comment: Brilliant gun simulator but it has issues. Half of the guns that have the ability to follow the shells and use ads don\'t hit the wall. The gun fires but nothing happens to the wall. Please fix.
reviews.author: Noah Hameroff

reviews.title: Upstate your app!
reviews.comment: Updates aren\'t frequent enough, I find myself getting bored of the app sometimes. If possible update the app every month or so.

reviews.comment: The gun was so realistic and its feel like real ones.Great game and awsome guns.Hope u have more guns coming soon. :)
